<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.7.9">
<l>pūvār tirumā makaḷpul kiyamārpā</l>
<l>nāvār pukaḻvē tiyarmaṉ ṉiyanāṅkūrt</l>
<l>tēvā tiruveḷ ḷa<supplied>k</supplied>kuḷat tuṟaivāṉē</l>
<l>yāvā vaṭiyā ṉivaṉeṉ ṟaruḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One whose chest is embraced by the great goddess,</l>
<l rend="indent">Tiru, who abides on a blossom,</l>
<l>God of Nāṅkūr where dwell Vedic experts whose praises abide on tongues,</l>
<l>One who dwells in Tiruveḷḷakkuḷam,</l>
<l>Saying, “Ah, ah, he is [my] servant,” be gracious.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
